OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing member of the
OL,4,Cpublic in Fareham
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for stabbing a
OL,7,Fmember of the public in Fareham last
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FPortsmouth Crown Court heard the 32-
OL,11,Fyear-old victim and his partner had
OL,12,Fbeen eating in a cafe on West Street
OL,13,Fwhen they noticed a man staring at
OL,14,Fthem on Monday 23 September.
OL,16,FAt around 11am they left the cafe and
OL,17,Fwere walking when the victim was
OL,18,Fstabbed in his back by the same man
OL,19,Fthey had seen earlier in the cafe.
