OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing member of the
OL,4,Cpublic in Fareham
OL,6,FThe couple ran to the police station
OL,7,Fon Quay Street where the victim was
OL,8,Fgiven immediate first aid and taken to
OL,9,Fa secure room.
OL,11,FThe man with the knife entered the
OL,12,Fpolice station shortly afterwards and
OL,13,Fhanded it across the counter. He was
OL,14,Fthen arrested by police officers.
OL,16,FSteven Colin Hardy, 44, of no fixed
OL,17,Faddress was subsequently charged and
OL,18,Fadmitted causing grievous bodily harm
OL,19,Fwith intent, possession of a knife in
OL,20,Fa public place, and possession of
OL,21,Fcannabis, prior to a planned trial.
