OL,6,FChief Inspector Marcus Kennedy,
OL,7,FDistrict Commander for Fareham, said:
OL,8,F"The quick actions of the Station
OL,9,FEnquiry Officers and members of our
OL,10,FNeighbourhood Policing Team helped to
OL,11,Fensure that the victim, his partner,
OL,12,For any other members of the public
OL,13,Fdidn't come to further harm following
OL,14,Fthis shocking incident.
OL,16,F"I'd like to thank them for their
OL,17,Fprofessionalism and dedication to
OL,18,Fpublic safety.
