OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing member of the
OL,4,Cpublic in Fareham
OL,6,F"Thankfully the victim's injuries were
OL,7,Fnot life threatening, but Hardy's
OL,8,Factions could have caused much more
OL,9,Fserious harm.
OL,11,F"I really do hope that this sentence
OL,12,Fhelps the victim and his partner to be
OL,13,Fable to move on with their lives safe
OL,14,Fin the knowledge that justice has been
OL,15,Fserved.
OL,17,F"We will continue to do all we can to
OL,18,Fensure that those who carry knives
OL,19,Fwill face the full consequences for
OL,20,Ftheir actions.
