OL,4,Cpublic in Fareham
OL,6,F"This case sends a strong message to
OL,7,Fanyone who chooses to carry a weapon
OL,8,For become involved in serious
OL,9,Fviolence, no good ever comes from it.
OL,11,F"The consequences can destroy lives
OL,12,Fforever."
OL,14,FHardy was sentenced to life
OL,15,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of
OL,16,Ffive years for causing grievous bodily
OL,17,Fharm with intent.
